data.oai_dc:dc: Harvest totals and harvest density (total animals trapped [2005-2013]/100 km2) for American martens and fishers, and fisher:marten ratio. Data collected at the scale of New York towns. Data must be joined to town boundary shapefile (also included) using BIOCOTOWN field to display data in GIS.
